name: The Eclipse Wall Unit
description: The Eclipse Wall Unit is the perfect marriage of form and function, creating a sophisticated backdrop for your home office while supplying elegant open storage to illustrate your unique character. Discover a sense of calm and tranquillity in your home with the luxurious and versatile Eclipse Home Office Collection. Fit for a CEO, the collection consists of the Eclipse luxurious Writing Desk, the Eclipse Wall Unit and a Fitted Alcove Unit to plan any home office layout.
